Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:27.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs28\shad0}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N受信赖的时间限制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看来训练出成果了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:36.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹长！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:41.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 曹长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这种距离的掩护还是头一次遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身手还过得去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪里射来的？伍长！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是山顶的炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且射得很准啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！被瞄准了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:06.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙里也有耳朵灵敏的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:09.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 敌人的着弹点迫近了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看来全体的位置都已被捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 情况不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:20.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,小队 散开后退 再议作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:21.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,正面有3个炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:35.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,战壕布置了ZAKU 再加上陡峭的山坡...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那条公路是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:42.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是补给维持方面最重要的公路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对联邦而言是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:49.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那里还是有办法过去的 问题是那村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被吉翁占领了很头痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:59.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,该如何应付那些利用自然地形而成的炮台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望能有支援啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:04.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等待职员的话 在这边会被逼入绝境的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:08.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:12.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沿着河绕道去西边的山坡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,突袭造成混乱的话 或许能行...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:19.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,说得倒轻松 那里是游击队出没的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:20.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,游击队？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 谁去奇袭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这瀑布我以前曾去过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奇袭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:37.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,反正只是诱敌的话 缺乏经验的队长也应该能行的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹长 这里就交由你来指挥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:41.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:44.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你那么说的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:49.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还有时间方面就定3小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:53.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会在3小时内到达目的地并发动奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们从正面牵制敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:56.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以防万一先申明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们进攻敌人等你回应最多只能坚持1小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:05.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹长以下4人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:09.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,于15时向公路方位前进 待机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等时间一到就发动总攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:12.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别被游击队什么的逮住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,游击队也是平民吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那些平民才是最可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这里也准备出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请多加小心 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:46.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能会在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,脱离战线了呢 少尉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不知死活的又回来啦 你这个色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这幸福的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,参观费啊 上次在瀑布的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,连我们都没看过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住 住手 误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？误会你什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:47.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,按住他 我来教训他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:48.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:49.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这是新货色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别弄啦 要是动起来了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:00.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,停 停下 快停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 别乱动啊 适可而...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:04.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱动的应该是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是想得到我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的军队都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,粗鲁 下流 肮脏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:25.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况你只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你还只是个小孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:38.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那为何那时一直盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要说为何... 只是因为很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:47.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间和你们纠缠了 让我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,BB 战斗进入了消耗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们处于极度的紧张感之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:01.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拍档艾历多亚对声纳寸不离耳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察着敌人的动静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在准备着下一次的进攻...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这种烂歌也能登上排行榜首
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:11.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,又在写情书了啦 你也很闲的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经准备好作战了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了你会被抛弃的 不要写了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:20.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你裸体的事我已经道歉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别作声快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了好几遍了 没时间和你们纠缠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也很忙的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:57.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 没时间了 要把我带到哪去...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:02.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊！我都说叫你住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去见老大 放规矩点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:29.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是BOSS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:40.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到我的地盘来有何贵干 西罗·阿玛达少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没经同意就过来是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在可是在作战行动中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:46.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:51.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你们来说没什么用 请放了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！有在听我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 请快点...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请问...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:06.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了 每天这个时间都有这习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:09.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 请认真听我说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,上面一片平静的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他们该不会是在喝下午茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:28.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹长 不知道队长平安到达了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:30.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他那么有自信应该没问题了 上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:31.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样说 你才能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:44.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们和联邦的共同敌人应该是吉翁才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:50.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,毁掉设在被占村子里的炮台对你们没什么坏处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:54.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了作战成功 同伴们在等着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,把村子从吉翁手上解放出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的同伴也能获得自由了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 放我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 尽管打过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还是放弃了吧 少尉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在老大面前 你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是我的首批部下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能让还没来得及熟悉的同伴们因我而阵亡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:39.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,放我走！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,确实确实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,利用这个家伙的话不就能把那个村子解放了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个村子里有我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:05.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不如趁此机会把吉翁那些家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:10.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 约定好了 我会解放村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:17.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多的病人和伤员很伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:20.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,药物的话要多少随便拿 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 吉翁那些家伙真无情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:26.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想要战利品吗 行啊 还我自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:33.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有比军人的约定更不可靠的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:34.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 琪琪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:36.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这家伙没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:38.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,欠我的债还没还呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别再嘿嘿哈哈地傻笑个不停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那好 爸爸 由我来监视他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:55.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然 不这样做你也不会听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:58.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉先生 现在我们休战如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拣回条小命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:05.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好好答谢小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:08.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琪琪 告诉少尉先生回去的路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,都成垃圾筒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候哪有闲工夫清理这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 毫不抵抗的人都要尽情殴打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:30.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要去的话就快点进来 没时间啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:36.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,敢有奇怪的举动的话 就这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:38.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我能对小孩子做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我可比你通人情世故得多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:41.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 把那个还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是我拿到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:48.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,3点半了！只剩下30分钟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你戴着也不合适呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫琪琪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:00.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琪琪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琪琪·洛基塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走吧 西罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我西罗... 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然被小孩子小看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别站在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要挺住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有没有什么捷径？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沿河前进虽然是最快的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:22.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没有路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚 上面有动静吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还听不出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要等到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到的话就完蛋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:48.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 队长的动静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 还确认不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:02.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:04.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,安静一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:05.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是队长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,1架 不 2架！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还过来？全队加强对空戒备！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:17.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧 这也是死神招来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:21.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,死神？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:22.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,臭名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诺里斯大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:32.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的部队很快就会收拾掉那些想爬上来的老鼠们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,损失了2台ZAKU吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:37.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,呃... 请向基尼亚斯阁下说点好话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:40.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是在特别视察日发生这种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:47.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他妹妹爱娜小姐听说非常美丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不... 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 都是因为相信了麻烦的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯 到极限了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,向公路方位后退！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:02.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹长！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会错 是队长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 总算开始了 坐稳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:18.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:25.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 让我好等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长真是个无所不能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:33.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是从那里 从河里发起的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想夹击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,马上放我下去 我用ZAKU出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 打中弹药库了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是少尉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你要下去的话就趁现在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要给你带路到最后结束才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快点出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 有2台ZAKU过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:44.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的1台过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭筒 给我打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!? 连游击队都加入了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,陷落只是时间问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,马撒德 撤退！我来拖延时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 北边的阻碍请由我来清除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我去收拾西边的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:33.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚 平民的疏散就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:49.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:50.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:52.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:55.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,游击队...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹长 能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起我来晚了 大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:03.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,解放村子 特别注意别伤到平民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,军曹 听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:16.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦和游击队的协同作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:36.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:03.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这个敌人有点本事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 到此为止了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道... 可没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:35.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:47.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:48.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有擅长水中战的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:03.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 在那里 要逃掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这个状态是无法纵深追击的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明明差一点就逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:16.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是大丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的收获真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:20.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为所欲为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是理所当然的权利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:25.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 你们还真是活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是无情的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:40.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们解放了这个村子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:42.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 再稍微感谢一下也好...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:48.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么... 你们想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:52.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶透了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:54.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这枪还真猛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:56.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 谁带了扳手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:58.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:03.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虏运送的车辆准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:03.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:05.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可这种光景...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:08.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么也得约束一下这些家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:12.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,约定好了的 让他们随便拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:14.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吧 约书亚曹长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:15.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 叫我卡莲就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我迟到了 对不起 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:22.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:27.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,西罗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:29.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:31.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友？怀表的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:34.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！不是！绝对不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:37.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人说服了游击队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:40.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(说了不是女朋友啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.70,0:24:19.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在西部区域的作战行动中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:23.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯向我们08小队提出了调职申请
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:26.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也听说过那个传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.55,0:24:28.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但没想到他会如此在意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.25,0:24:32.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我们遭遇了难以想像的东西
